        "TileImage": "$($repository 913e88c7-36ce-45fc-81aa-09b7c2853022).Image",
        "Description": "Apologies 47, we had a bit of a mix up with our Club 27 contract.  \r\rThe intended targets are a different Morgan and Cross.  It is also Nicholas Cross&#39;s birthday, and he did not want to steal Jordan&#39;s thunder today.\r\rHis lawyer, Morgan Fleming is here to surprise him with news of his inheritance from Cross&#39;s recently deceased uncle - a scheme and murder initiated by these two.\r\rThe family wants their money and revenge.\r\rGood luck, 47",
